OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1778760670
OL,3,CUK economy grew 0.3% in March despite
OL,4,CUS war in Iran
OL,6,FThe UK economy grew by 0.3% in March
OL,7,Fdespite the US-Israeli war on Iran,
OL,8,FONS data has shown.
OL,10,FThe Office for National Statistics
OL,11,F(ONS) reported a 0.3% rise in March,
OL,12,Fbeating predictions that the Middle
OL,13,FEast conflict would shrink the economy
OL,14,Fby 0.1% or 0.2%.
OL,16,FIt follows growth of 0.4% in February
OL,17,Fand 0% in January, revised down from
OL,18,F0.5% and 0.1% previously estimated.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
