OL,3,CUK economy grew 0.3% in March despite
OL,4,CUS war in Iran
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FOverall, there was a 0.6% rise in GDP
OL,12,Ffor the first quarter of the year, the
OL,13,FONS said.
OL,15,FThis was mostly powered by the
OL,16,Fservices sector, which grew by 0.8%
OL,17,Fcompared to 0.4% across construction
OL,18,Fand 0.2% across production.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
