OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1778760670
OL,3,CUK economy grew 0.3% in March despite
OL,4,CUS war in Iran
OL,6,FThe largest positive contributor to
OL,7,Fgrowth was wholesale and retail trade,
OL,8,Fwith the repair of motor vehicles and
OL,9,Fmotorbikes increasing by 2%.
OL,11,FThe largest negative contributor was
OL,12,Fadministrative and support service
OL,13,Factivities, which fell by 1% due to
OL,14,F"declines in rental and leasing
OL,15,Factivities, and employment
OL,16,Factivities", the ONS said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
