OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1778760670
OL,3,CUK economy grew 0.3% in March despite
OL,4,CUS war in Iran
OL,6,F"Growth picked up in the first quarter
OL,7,Fof the year, led by broad-based
OL,8,Fincreases across the services sector,"
OL,9,Fsaid Liz McKeown, ONS director of
OL,10,Feconomic statistics.
OL,12,F"Within that wholesale, computer
OL,13,Fprogramming and advertising performed
OL,14,Fparticularly well.
OL,16,F"Production also grew slightly, while
OL,17,Fconstruction returned to growth,
OL,18,Fthough only partly reversing weakness
OL,19,Fat the end of last year."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@AOU{D@YO]
